originalSql:
SELECT 
    s.s_name AS supplier_name,
    p.p_name AS part_name,
    p.p_brand AS part_brand,
    SUM(ps.ps_availqty) AS total_available_quantity,
    AVG(l.l_extendedprice) AS avg_extended_price,
    COUNT(DISTINCT c.c_custkey) AS unique_customers,
    r.r_name AS region_name
FROM 
    supplier s
JOIN 
    partsupp ps ON s.s_suppkey = ps.ps_suppkey
JOIN 
    part p ON ps.ps_partkey = p.p_partkey
JOIN 
    lineitem l ON p.p_partkey = l.l_partkey
JOIN 
    orders o ON l.l_orderkey = o.o_orderkey
JOIN 
    customer c ON o.o_custkey = c.c_custkey
JOIN 
    nation n ON s.s_nationkey = n.n_nationkey
JOIN 
    region r ON n.n_regionkey = r.r_regionkey
WHERE 
    s.s_comment LIKE '%reliable%'
    AND p.p_type LIKE '%metal%'
    AND l.l_shipdate BETWEEN DATE '1997-01-01' AND DATE '1997-12-31'
GROUP BY 
    s.s_name, p.p_name, p.p_brand, r.r_name
HAVING 
    SUM(ps.ps_availqty) > 50
ORDER BY 
    total_available_quantity DESC, avg_extended_price ASC

SELECT COALESCE("SUPPLIER_NAME", "SUPPLIER_NAME") AS "SUPPLIER_NAME", "PART_NAME", "PART_BRAND", "TOTAL_AVAILABLE_QUANTITY", "AVG_EXTENDED_PRICE", "UNIQUE_CUSTOMERS", "REGION_NAME"
FROM (SELECT "SUPPLIER_NAME", "PART_NAME", "PART_BRAND", "TOTAL_AVAILABLE_QUANTITY", "AVG_EXTENDED_PRICE", "UNIQUE_CUSTOMERS", "REGION_NAME"
FROM (SELECT "t1"."s_name", "t2"."p_name", "t2"."p_brand", "region"."r_name", MIN("t1"."s_name") AS "SUPPLIER_NAME", MIN("t2"."p_name") AS "PART_NAME", MIN("t2"."p_brand") AS "PART_BRAND", SUM("partsupp"."ps_availqty") AS "TOTAL_AVAILABLE_QUANTITY", AVG("s1"."l_extendedprice") AS "AVG_EXTENDED_PRICE", COUNT(DISTINCT "customer"."c_custkey") AS "UNIQUE_CUSTOMERS", MIN("region"."r_name") AS "REGION_NAME"
FROM "region"
INNER JOIN "nation" ON "region"."r_regionkey" = "nation"."n_regionkey"
INNER JOIN (SELECT *
FROM "supplier"
WHERE "s_comment" LIKE '%reliable%') AS "t1" ON "nation"."n_nationkey" = "t1"."s_nationkey"
INNER JOIN ((SELECT *
FROM "part"
WHERE "p_type" LIKE '%metal%') AS "t2" INNER JOIN "partsupp" ON "t2"."p_partkey" = "partsupp"."ps_partkey") ON "t1"."s_suppkey" = "partsupp"."ps_suppkey"
INNER JOIN ("customer" INNER JOIN ("s1" INNER JOIN "orders" ON "s1"."l_orderkey" = "orders"."o_orderkey") ON "customer"."c_custkey" = "orders"."o_custkey") ON "t2"."p_partkey" = "s1"."l_partkey"
GROUP BY "region"."r_name", "t1"."s_name", "t2"."p_name", "t2"."p_brand") AS "t4"
WHERE "t4"."TOTAL_AVAILABLE_QUANTITY" > 50
ORDER BY "TOTAL_AVAILABLE_QUANTITY" DESC NULLS FIRST, "AVG_EXTENDED_PRICE") AS "t7"
